2026-05-10T22:47:23.8831905Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-10T22:47:23.8832703Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-10T22:47:23.8833514Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-10T22:47:23.8834322Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-10T22:47:23.8835136Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-10T22:47:23.8836095Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
